title: Sefer shene luḥot ha-berit
creator: Horoṿits, Yesha'yah Ben Avraham ha-Levi
subject: Historische Drucke
source: Horoṿits, Yesha'yah Ben Avraham ha-Levi: Sefer shene luḥot ha-berit  amarot ṭehorot, mifnenim yiḳarot, ḥibur ʿal shete torot, be-ketav ụ-be-peh mesine masurat, ʿarukhot ʿve-sedorot .... Franḳfurṭ de-Odra  Franḳfurṭ de-Odra  Berlin 1717
alternative: amarot ṭehorot, mifnenim yiḳarot, ḥibur ʿal shete torot, be-ketav ụ-be-peh mesine masurat, ʿarukhot ʿve-sedorot ...
